| `toolUseResult` + `renderToolResultMessage` | `events.build_tool_completed_sse_payload` + `tool_display.format_tool_display_excerpt` |
| `processToolResultBlock` | `run_tool_use` + `truncate_tool_result` |
| `renderToolResultMessage` / `extractSearchText` | `tools/tool.py` `ui_excerpt` + `tool_ui.py` |
